     under the quotation mark delimiting the subject. For exam-
     ple,

          "abcdefgh" ? (tab(0) & snapshot())

     produces

          -------------------------
          |                       |
          | &subject = "abcdefgh" |
          |                     | |
          -------------------------

     Escape sequences are handled properly. For example,

          "abc\tdef\nghi" ? (tab(upto('\n')) & snapshot())

     produces

          ------------------------------
